{"tid":1439282,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"出trip慘過牙痛","createTime":"2019-08-10T05:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T05:16:55.000Z","uid":88491,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ec63c2945a7e1c276d6a85fa67b1cfbd7e00eef6","tid":1439282,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:07:08.000Z","msg":"開始搭飛機搭到有恐懼感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n工作關係平均一至兩個月要飛一次 <br />\n最癲試過每星期飛一次（day trip ) 去到開個會又飛返黎 來回都八個鐘  三餐都係機場/飛機餐搞掂 係飛機都無得抖下 要開住部notebook on99係到趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n親戚/朋友聽到我又飛好似以為我去玩<br />\n又叫我代購呢樣個樣 ，唔好話咩名勝古蹟 ，有時連附近條街都無機會行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 又要飛 我屌撚爆你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"897fdd596bd4c7bc90be1a34bbe317acb7a79970","tid":1439282,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:09:08.000Z","msg":"猁猁miss u<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc266ce18dd59e24475b841372cd69038fb5896a","tid":1439282,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:11:42.000Z","msg":"幾錢人工先<br />\n<br />\n低既話你好抵請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11b1afe67a56e3597c99914325ca1c57154e5eb","tid":1439282,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc266ce18dd59e24475b841372cd69038fb5896a","tid":1439282,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:11:42.000Z","msg":"幾錢人工先<br />\n<br />\n低既話你好抵請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:12:22.000Z","msg":"佢做緊我隻私家鴨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe6af186f9dadf98c0e1364a41f9f180e05047e","tid":1439282,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"897fdd596bd4c7bc90be1a34bbe317acb7a79970","tid":1439282,"uid":143093,"like":1,"di